fields.title: Le Paris
fields.description: Le Paris was created in homage of the style and sophistication that the city exudes every moment. This Parisian Blue double beasted suit jacket pairs incredibly well with bright contrasting hues of red and purple.
fields.content: Le Paris was created in homage of the style and sophistication that the city exudes every moment. This Parisian Blue double beasted suit jacket pairs incredibly well with bright contrasting hues of red and purple.

fields.title: The Classic
fields.description: The suit all others are compared to... Classic, Modern. Work, Night-Out; this suit fits the bill exceptionally. If you only have one suit in your quiver, make it THE CLASSIC. The inherent versatility of the two button, notched lapel design along with AirBespoke's invertable pocket flap architecture cement THE CLASSIC as the classy style for any occasion.

fields.title: Al Casablanca
fields.description: Elegance, Sophistication, Style; all come to mind in regards to Casablanca. Don't just wear our most contemporary take on modern Black Tie formal, embody it completely. THE CASABLANCA brings a certain urbane suave impossible to be matched by the local tailor or Men's Warehouse's of the world.

fields.title: De Brussel
fields.description: Power and Prestige. Few looks in the world can trump the unrestrained expression of the DE BRUSSEL. The inspiration of this one of a kind sapphire blue, Italian Cashmere suit originates from Brussels Belgium; where European Heads of State, capitalist figureheads, and global taste makers convene to transform the world daily.

fields.title: Classic White
fields.description: AirBespoke button-down shirts are woven from soft, wrinkle-resistant 100% Italian cotton. Our Tailors cut and sew AirBespoke shirts to your exacting standards and finish them with all details you’ve come to expect: a button-down collar, removable collar stays, reinforced buttons and seams, and double-button barrel cuffs. Pair this shirt with some denim and a sharp blazer to make a statement on your next date or board meeting. Don’t hesitate to wear them with chinos as well--these versatile button-ups dress up with ease.
